  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Team Leader",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Job Title: Service Team Leader</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead daily operations with clarity, ensuring smooth shifts and high team morale.</p></li><li><p>Step up as the on-the-floor leader, providing direction and stability when needed.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain a warm, welcoming atmosphere that guests feel the moment they arrive.</p></li><li><p>Handle surprises gracefully, turning small challenges into opportunities to impress.</p></li><li><p>Mentor and motivate the team, helping each member grow and excel.</p></li><li><p>Foster a positive, high-energy environment where teamwork comes naturally.</p></li><li><p>Uphold our highest standards of service, quality, and presentation.</p></li><li><p>Continuously look for ways to improve our operation and guest experience.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You Bring:</strong></p><ul><li><p>A true passion for teamwork and pride in doing things well.</p></li><li><p>Experience in food & beverage, or a strong eagerness to learn quickly.</p></li><li><p>An authentic love for people and service, evident in your actions.</p></li><li><p>Flexibility to work a 5-day rotating schedule, including weekends and holidays.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
